{"tid":1461260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］816撳錢 廣傳俾姨媽姑姐 師奶親戚聽","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:18:42.000Z","uid":56711,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8eca5b05a83e5ad4d5a75f429d420eed509fb36e","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"暫時見到文宣圖會係以唔撳錢結果 未發生嘅事作宣傳<br />\n<br />\n日常返工時間最得閒去銀行排隊會係咩人？<br />\n<br />\n如果改變到方向成為<br />\n好多人想撳晒啲錢出嚟<br />\n等銀行無錢咁<br />\n或者係同呢兩日機場有關<br />\n先最好入到師奶們嘅耳仔<br />\n係咪應該代入師奶心理諗諗？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實消息流通最快嘅<br />\n唔係連登 唔係tvb <br />\n係無腦分享嘅WhatsApp</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n我見證住上星期五<br />\n公司啊叔師奶已經比我呢個長期睇連登嘅人<br />\n更早收到風話星期一塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一次屋企附近放映會<br />\n我上Facebook 都未見到消息<br />\n我老母一早就已經叫我早啲返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得有一次東亞傳新聞<br />\n真係有班人去擠提？<br />\n<br />\n今次如果想事成<br />\n對公眾 尤其是比較無知嘅一班<br />\n一定要通知大部分師奶發揚光大<br />\n同時要讓佢地聽得入耳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">當然 我地當日得閒都要去排排隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最怕就有銀行排出門口情況啦<br />\n尤其是公屋邨附近啲銀行又細細間多人經過<br />\n<br />\n一陣好似新年換新銀紙咁<br />\n俾師奶見到<br />\n又要落嚟同我地爭住撳錢 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n暫時仲諗緊排隊銀行撳幾多錢好<br />\n撳幾多次錢好<br />\n等我搵下屋企本簿仔先<br />\n<br />\n全力支持中銀<br />\n最愛中銀嘅一百 五百蚊紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de18e040af42b06ac19e0ab326807a6dd4bab757","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"請關懷身邊有中銀戶口但無錢嘅朋友<br />\n有無人差十蚊廿蚊夠錢撳一百蚊出嚟啊？<br />\n轉數快方便喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9650e23b3bb5cdf7098ae34e822ff4dd8ef4ab6","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"901184f766c80097f0868255ed2b8e0513375618","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台<br />\n係咪應該開財經台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4408d4ccdf7873ef06a78d09c61f8f3dd3bb0ac9","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc931e9e88250de9aac41025f1c2f154b105d94b","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e3860cd79f3f5e17db0ffe9216384d36e65741","tid":1461260,"uid":110568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"先撳中資銀行，再用轉數快轉走啲錢，增加佢哋成本"},{"pid":"ccacd9b3a4ef8cc974163fbc9632a0c52da6fb8f","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ebd50a579e19a1af56e9d1231362fa44555e27","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94380ac2e52ab9a92a346442cdec8b6540c24d7f","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded9f77afcf7f81983b68ffbed846d6b40946ae4","tid":1461260,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:08:20.